These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, paramedic
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, spanish
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter
1. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the architect is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | juice    |
| Job           | paramedic | architect |
| Nationality   | argentine       | spanish  |
| Transport     | jet-ski      | scooter     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, potato
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, rock
2 different pets are kept: fish, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the person driving the train is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | potato | eggplant |
| Music-Genre   | electronic       | rock         |
| Pet           | hamster     | fish         |
| Transport     | train    | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, engineer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, train
1. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
4. the person driving the train is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking          | gardening |
| Job           | engineer | mechanic     |
| Music-Genre   | classical            | pop         |
| Transport     | train         | van   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, d&b
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | western |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | d&b |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | rabbit    |

