2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the colombian##1
4. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | country      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | colombian   |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | ice-hockey |

