.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee
There 2 different types of food: cherry, pepper
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, funk
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating cherry is the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | coffee     | mirinda |
| Food          | pepper   | cherry |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | gospel     |
| Transport     | roller | tram     |

 